<!-- SEO ARTICLE -->
<section class="article-section">
<div class="ctr">
<div class="badge badge-dark">INSIGHTS</div>
<h2>3PL Logistics in Ukraine: What International Brands Need to Know</h2>
<div class="article-content">
<h3>Why 3PL matters for entering the Ukrainian market</h3>
<p>Ukraine is a fast-growing e-commerce market with over 40 million consumers. For international brands entering this market, setting up in-house logistics is expensive and risky &mdash; local labour laws, infrastructure challenges, and power outages require local expertise. A 3PL partner like MTP Group handles warehousing, picking, packing, shipping via Nova Poshta and other local carriers, plus returns processing. You focus on sales and marketing while we handle everything from CRM integration to last-mile delivery.</p>

<h3>CRM integration: seamless order flow</h3>
<p>MTP Group integrates with Shopify, WooCommerce, KeyCRM, Horoshop, and Prom.ua within 2 hours. Orders flow automatically from your CRM to the warehouse. Picking follows WMS-optimised routes, items are barcode-scanned and packed per your specifications, then handed to the carrier. Tracking updates flow back to your CRM automatically &mdash; zero manual data entry. See all <a href="/en/services/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">available services</a> for details.</p>

<h3>Infrastructure resilience since 2022</h3>
<p>Since the start of the full-scale invasion, MTP Group has operated without a single day of downtime. Three backup generators, Starlink satellite internet, and dual fibre connections ensure uninterrupted operations through any blackout. Two warehouse facilities near Kyiv (3,700 m&sup2; total) provide the capacity to handle 60,000+ shipments per month. This level of resilience is critical for brands that cannot afford delivery delays.</p>

<h3>Cost advantage of Ukrainian 3PL</h3>
<p>Fulfilment costs in Ukraine start from 18 UAH (approximately $0.45 USD) per shipment at scale &mdash; significantly lower than Western European or US 3PL rates. Storage runs from 650 UAH/m&sup3;/month. For brands shipping to Ukrainian consumers, this means higher margins without compromising service quality. Use our <a href="/en/calculator/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">cost calculator</a> for a precise quote, and read <a href="/en/recalls/" style="color:#e63329;font-weight:500">client testimonials</a> from brands already operating with us.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

